title: Painting Essentials: Thinning Paints
description:
One of the fundamental parts of painting is learning to thin your paints. In this video, we'll be showing you how to thin your paints so that you can achieve that smooth finish!    
    
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
